  "fields": {
    "apply_url": "https://jobs.ashbyhq.com/monad.foundation/dccd3d0f-e491-45fa-b311-980021976d62/application",
    "company": "Monad Foundation",
    "compensation": "",
    "content_hash": "fc899166b862745f",
    "department": "Business Development",
    "description": "The Monad Foundation is a team of dedicated ecosystem and community builders who are on a mission to massively grow the impact of decentralized tech. We believe that the Monad https://monad.xyz/ blockchain--the performant and parallel EVM Layer 1--will help decentralized apps eat the world.\n\n\nTHE ROLE\n\nWe’re looking for a Business Development Lead to position Monad Foundation’s efforts to build out the payments ecosystem. This is an entrepreneurial, high-autonomy role for someone who thrives on building from zero, identifying opportunities, forming partnerships, and creating momentum around a new standard in crypto payments.\n\n\nWHAT YOU’LL DO\n\n - Ecosystem Building: Identify, engage, and onboard key ecosystem partners including fintechs, PSPs, banks, and stablecoin issuers.\n   \n\n - Partnerships and Deals: Structure and negotiate agreements that drive adoption of Monad as a global settlement payments layer.\n   \n\n - GTM Execution: Collaborate on launch strategy, including the marketing narrative, landing page, and early customer integrations.\n   \n\n - Market Development: Evangelize Monad to the broader crypto and fintech communities through events, partnerships, and strategic outreach.\n   \n\n - Research and Insight: Rapidly get up the curve on stablecoins, payments, and settlements to inform strategy and execution.\n   \n\n\nWHO YOU ARE\n\n - Track record closing marquee deals in fintech, payments and/or traditional finance sectors\n\n - Deep curiosity about stablecoins, payments, and the intersection of crypto and fintech.\n\n - Hustler mindset; you make things happen even with limited structure.\n\n - Strong network or demonstrated ability to build one quickly in crypto and fintech circles.\n\n - Excellent communicator and storyteller who can move between technical and business contexts.\n\n - Comfortable taking ownership and operating autonomously.\n\n - Based in or willing to relocate to New York City or San Francisco.\n   \n\n\nWHY JOIN\n\n - Strategic focus. Shape one of the most ambitious projects at Monad Foundation, the Internet Payment Network.\n\n - Seat at the table. Work directly with Monad Foundation leadership on go-to-market strategy and ecosystem growth.\n\n - Where the action is. Build relationships at the forefront of fintech and crypto adoption.\n\n\nWHY WORK WITH US\n\n - Challenging problems. You’ll work on extremely challenging problems with massive impact.\n\n - Huge opportunity. The Ethereum Virtual Machine (EVM) standard is ubiquitous, but existing EVM-compatible chains are slow and bandwidth-constrained. Monad’s core innovations offer developers the best of both worlds (portability and performance) and are a game-changer for mass user adoption in crypto.\n\n - The right team. You’ll be part of an exceptional and highly-motivated team\n\n - Culture. We’re a lean team working together to achieve very ambitious goals. We are united in our culture of collaboration, low ego, and high-quality output. As an early member of our team, you’ll help continue to shape our culture.",
    "employment_type": "FullTime",
